				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">First of all... hello everyone.  I've been reading this forum for a long time, but I've yet to make a post.  Just to let you all know, I've found this to be the best place for me to to pick up tips on how to play my mage.  I just wanted to say thanks for all the amazing info.
<br />

<br />
And now, to try to pry some people for a little more...
<br />

<br />
As of the August 11 patch, hotspot zones have been changed.  City of Mist is now listed as a hotspot for levels 40-45.  I just dinged 44 and picked up my new spells, and was about to start looking for places to hunt before this change.  With the hotspot change, seems like CoM would be the place to go.  However, the only post regarding CoM is one about getting PL'ed by a 65 shammy... which isn't an option for me.  I was wondering if anyone would have any hunting tips for this zone, especially for a soloing mage.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
