				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I know it's a bit late, but I thought I'd add my 2 cents.
<br />

<br />
Best advice I could give you is go in with a healer (any will do), and 2 or 3 dps (1 or 2 besides you). Tanks are OPTIONAL! That's right, OPTIONAL! if you have a couple necros or, especially, mages.
<br />

<br />
Way I went in was 2 mages, one wizard, 2 clerics, and a tank. The dps's easily took out the mobs as fast as I could cast my dd spell! Truly awesome.<br />_________________<br />Do you wish to challenge me, sir?!
